  "title": "7506 - Gardener | Plant Nursery / Landscape Worker | Novena",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF</strong></li><li><strong>8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $1,950 [ Fix ]</strong></li><li><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits & Bonus</strong></li></ul><p><em><strong>This role will work under Landscaping & Plantation Company but outsource to work under various hospitals in Singapore. [ Novena ]</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Must be Covid vaccination certified due to the work environment at hospitals.</li><li>Prefer those with basic plantation knowledge and gardener experience.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Scopes:</strong></p><ol><li>Weeding and mulching landscape beds</li><li>Trimming small trees, hedges and shrubs</li><li>Removing unwanted, dead or damaged trees</li><li>Planting shrubs, flowers and trees</li><li>Watering gardens, lawns and landscapes</li><li>Grass cutting</li><li>Fertilizing plants</li><li>Monitoring and maintaining plant health</li></ol><p><br /></p><p><strong>Chin See Min Reg No. : R22107450</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No. : 14C7279</strong></p>",
